      <a href="https://orangette.net/2007/06/how-it-works/#comment-8374"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2007-06-11T18:22:00-04:00">Monday, June 11, 2007 at 6:22 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>oh my&#8230;i jotted this down and carried it around a few days until i absolutely couldn&#8217;t stand it&#8230;i bought just so-so tomatoes and was a bit concerned. but it was SO tasty. at first i was a bit concerned about how much it made, but it was gone in less than 2 days! (that&#8217;s with only 2 ppl). i think this will be made many more times!!</p>
    </div>

